description: 30 minutes is all it takes to whip up this mouth-watering chicken parmigiana that’s full of spring flavours. The basil pesto, asparagus and mozzarella coating on the schnitzel will send tastebuds into overdrive with each satisfying crunch.
keywords: Parmigiana,Nicky,Seafood free,Low salt,Gluten free,Egg free,Low sugar,Schnitzel & parmigiana,Sesame free,Budget,High protein,Soy free,Wheat free,Chicken,Asparagus
name: Spring Chicken Parmigiana Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 bunch asparagus, trimmed halved lengthways and crossways

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 230°C/210°C fan-forced. Line a large baking tray with baking paper. Arrange schnitzel on tray. Bake for 10 minutes or until golden.

Remove schnitzel from oven and spread each schnitzel with a little pesto and sprinkle with half the mozzarella. Arrange asparagus on top and sprinkle with remaining mozzarella. Season with pepper. Bake for 10 minutes or until golden and chicken is cooked through.
Sprinkle with basil leaves and season with pepper. Serve with spinach and rocket.
